/**
 * Module Name: Likes
 * Module Description: Give visitors an easy way to show their appreciation for your content.
 * First Introduced: 2.2
 * Sort Order: 23
 * Requires Connection: Yes
 * Auto Activate: No
 * Module Tags: Social
